            div.portfolioWriteUp
                li Combat mission inside an imperial AT-AT factory where the player eventually takes control of an AT-AT and wrecks havoc
                    ul.nested
                        li.nested Finalized the layout for the imperial factory, giving players insight into AT-AT manufacturing.
                        li.nested Designed key combat areas, providing players with multiple approaches for sneaking or fighting through the level.
                        li.nested Scripted objectives where players shut down the factory, take control of an AT-AT, and escape across the surface of Sullust.
                





